gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擔心會唔會辯方喺度搞搞陣博個官程序錯或者出現偏頗情況，然後用呢個原因上訴打甩仲好"},{"pid":"cbccdc3b9667a15deba3382370849549121e9d26","tid":463862,"uid":124499,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錢官睇黎都唔係好妥辯方果邊</blockquote><br />\n大佬呀 片都有埋 你點打甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「係，我係打市民，<br />\n但呢單案既重點係我先識戰術訓練！」<br />\n<br />\n得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n呢度案嘅重點唔係我有冇打市民，而係浪子回頭金不換啊法官大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18771cd94a727af73fa9a1b8500643747f347239","tid":463862,"uid":58552,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"咁on9嘅律師 除左cctvb d劇見過外 真係第一次見"},{"pid":"31508a936c7a7bfd8bf3152f0d2924fa3c4f89c1","tid":463862,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日話佔中要剎一警百，亂打市民就好坐一個刹一警百啦</blockquote><br />\n殺一儆百"},{"pid":"c1d42612905f087d3a83d05254be5840d4b6451d","tid":463862,"uid":148332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171110/20209957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F20209957&d=8o8IpGvZIrFUzz0L7rZ4FjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=819b6f80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F20209957&h=d750fdf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171110/20209957</a><br />\n<br />\n欲示範揮警棍遭官拒絕<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n    <br />\n   <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171110/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171110%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=f3b069f6&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】朱經緯昨差點有機會公開表演案發當日如何揮動警棍，其代表大律師彭彼得將與涉案同類型警棍交給他，要求他示範，但主任裁判官錢禮（圖）自言可在呈堂錄影片段看到朱如何揮動警棍，不用朱示範。控方資深大律師麥禮士笑言，可考慮在辯方大狀身上示範如何用警棍。<br />\n<br />\n官質疑自辯如上戰術堂<br />\n<br />\n同屬警隊出身的彭將警棍交給朱後，特意「溫馨提示」朱要冷靜，不要重蹈他日前在庭上以棍敲枱遭官訓斥的覆轍。錢官稱不用朱示範後，書記聞言即收回警棍。<br />\n<br />\n對於朱在庭上長篇大論解釋如何應付群眾聚集，錢官亦表不滿，指被告自辯一天半仍未講到涉案關鍵情節，質疑「我們是否在上戰術堂」，直言<span style=\"color: red;\">容忍也有限度</span>，要求彭控制聆訊進度及被告作供方向。其後彭引述《公安條例》條文時，錢官再要求他加快提問速度。彭聞言喃喃自語：「如果沒有這麼多騷擾的話&hellip;&hellip;」錢官淡淡的問彭：「你是向我說話嗎？」彭說不是。<br />\n<br />\n朱承認曾用警棍打事主鄭仲恒，但強調理由包括鄭不服從指令及向其他警員作出侵略性動作。朱自告奮勇示範鄭當時的表情和動作，挺胸揚手，雙腳微微分開，頭部大幅度急促搖向右邊，朱的姿態頗似電影《少林足球》中演員田啟文所做的假動作。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊家樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我舊豬膶呢?係咪你食左"},{"pid":"0b97497ffa29c2032c248e24e161e457eff2c918","tid":463862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>控方資深大律師麥禮士笑言，可考慮在辯方大狀身上示範如何用警棍。<br />\n<br />\nMarash明寸9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家香港係法庭係用英文定廣東話</blockquote><br />\n應該兩樣都得"},{"pid":"5815108288713fec7fb7d54bef8c4b6d3ac2a97d","tid":463862,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>控方資深大律師麥禮士笑言，可考慮在辯方大狀身上示範如何用警棍。<br />\n<br />\nMarash明寸9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家香港係法庭係用英文定廣東話</blockquote><br />\n應該兩樣都得</blockquote><br />\n係兩樣都得但都會揀其中一樣<br />\n唔會講講下英文又轉中文"},{"pid":"99f774734823a47d03e67b0bd69196bd66451025","tid":463862,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"究竟呢單野係法庭好笑啲定碌撚審狼英搞笑啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f750fbf91040ac4188624ce3746ea9cd607c8a","tid":463862,"uid":8009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"唉 柒警點解會放返出黎"},{"pid":"7ddf8c60f9679f81a08fcf1af899642fd56d485a","tid":463862,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"點解警察裝備可以隨便拎到上庭<br />\n定果支有label到係證物 係果日鏡頭影住果支?"},{"pid":"f4390edb43195eda3f8b6917ef7b2e2e57ebd2ed","tid":463862,"uid":9230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>控方資深大律師麥禮士笑言，可考慮在辯方大狀身上示範如何用警棍。<br />\n<br />\nMarash明寸9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家香港係法庭係用英文定廣東話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錢禮係印藉，兩邊律師都係鬼佬，所以開英文台<br />\n<br />\n不過錢禮本人係識聽廣東話嘅"},{"pid":"aaffb64ee7d19a0d7b60fd96ee7f0b0c22a1efd9","tid":463862,"uid":157415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"邊到開庭？想去聽"},{"pid":"b32477b1707e157fea4c5637292fa26221671f84","tid":463862,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錢官睇黎都唔係好妥辯方果邊</blockquote><br />\n大佬呀 片都有埋 你點打甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知入就入硬, 係擔心個官可能共底, 會輕判<br />\n而家睇到個官好似冇特別優待辯方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擔心會唔會辯方喺度搞搞陣博個官程序錯或者出現偏頗情況，然後用呢個原因上訴打甩仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錢禮唔係釘官，佢審案算公道"},{"pid":"6939fbed78b860c52d187eb27619d7d796128b62","tid":463862,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到開庭？想去聽</blockquote><br />\n法 庭<br />\nCourt :<br />\n第八庭  四樓 No.8  (4/F)   <br />\n裁判官<br />\nMagistrate :<br />\n錢禮主任裁判官  Ms. Bina CHAINRAI, Principal Magist