7-11-10T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"Ms Bina Chainrai<br />\n<br />\n     Ms Chainrai was born in India in 1957. She obtained LL.B. and P.C.LL. from the University of Hong Kong in 1980 and 1981 respectively. She further acquired a Diploma in Chinese Law from the University of East Asia, Macau in 1989. She was called to the Bar in Hong Kong in 1982 and in the United Kingdom in 1985. She was in private practice between 1982 and 1990. She was appointed as a Permanent Magistrate in 1990.<br />\n<br />\n讀港大咁耐<br />\n又喺澳門大學讀過Chinese Law<br />\n應該點都識少少中文"},{"pid":"43df6c80218336df6f618d915205fb719e2ef3f9","tid":463862,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪呀朱經緯！"},{"pid":"c184707e9bc01a31bf69b1f572b5930dbe031076","tid":463862,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ms Bina Chainrai<br />\n<br />\n     Ms Chainrai was born in India in 1957. She obtained LL.B. and P.C.LL. from the University of Hong Kong in 1980 and 1981 respectively. She further acquired a Diploma in Chinese Law from the University of East Asia, Macau in 1989. She was called to the Bar in Hong Kong in 1982 and in the United Kingdom in 1985. She was in private practice between 1982 and 1990. She was appointed as a Permanent Magistrate in 1990.<br />\n<br />\n讀港大咁耐<br />\n又喺澳門大學讀過Chinese Law<br />\n應該點都識少少中文</blockquote><br />\n呢個好煩，到好深入，但都算明事理嘅，唔似共<br />\n尤其個差佬咁鳩辯，呢個官真係會屌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cac66c2272375318298230557f00060d4f48d2","tid":463862,"uid":125464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"下次衰強姦既話..."},{"pid":"ef7496d51641988c4e376e3fa159c4e8fa8a4f96","tid":463862,"uid":34760,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>辯方律師本身係半桶水律師，唔知邊個陷害朱蛇提議佢請條咁嘅友。本身都入硬咁濟，有呢條友加多腳，隨時罪加一等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal